        <h3>Accomodation</h3>
        <p>Weather you are just one person, a couple, a group or a family: We have the perfect options for you to stay. Right next to the beach with a beautiful ocaen view, an authentic building with beautiful old tiles and details... Check out the rooms and the terrace.</p>
