        <h3>Holiday Packages</h3>
        <p>What is your dream holiday come true? We offer many options and services.
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Surf Camps</strong> including boards, wetsuits, lessons and trips to different surfspots</li>
            <li><strong>Culture Holidays</strong> inlcuding cooking classes, drum concerts, sight seeing trips</li>
            <li><strong>Wellness and Yoga</strong> including healthy smoothies, yoga lessons, morning meditation, hammam and massages</li>
