        <h3>Get around</h3>
        <p>You want to see other places in the area? Come and book trips to the most beautiful places around. For example a day in Paradise Valley. It is a djungle like valley 40 minutes from Taghazout with a canyon with beautiful natural swimming pools of fresh mountain water and high palm trees and flowers. Our day trip includes the way there and back, a tasty tajine for lunch there and some refreshing and healthy snacks. </p>
        <p>Another interesting day trip is the journey through the Souk of Agadir. "Souk" stands for a bazar with many stands of traditional Moroccan handcraft, huge pyramides of different spices, handpressed Amlou (traditional Moroccan Almond-Honey-Paste), magical carpets and teapots, dried figgs, dates and Arabic spice coffee and much more... Our day trip to the Souk includes the transport, some historical guidance and fair prices for whatever you wish to buy.</p>
        <div class="btn btn-default"><%= link_to 'Show more', places_show_path, id: "button-default" %></div> 
